snippet.textDisplay:
Two lovers, Javed and Husna, (from Lahore) were supposed to get married in 1947, but couldn't. After partition, Husna stayed back in Lahore while Javed came to India and resided in Lucknow. In the 60's, Javed (having been married and father of 2 kids) writes a letter to Husna to know of the changes at her country - eager to know conditions prevailing in the new-born nation asking 'What did we achieve from partition !'. 

Source: Piyush Mishra

Melodious, nostalgic, superb ! Love the song !
snippet.textOriginal:
